overview:
Monkey Doctor is an international sales agency and television consultancy. Representing finished programming in genres of drama, documentary, lifestyle and current affairs, Monkey Doctor serves as a distributor to broadcasters worldwide specializing in emerging markets. Monkey Doctor also develops new drama and lifestyle series, working with like-minded partners around the world. The companyâ€™s representatives have established relationships globally and have a proven track record in sales as a result of a decade of experience in film and television.

Selective in its content and clientele, Monkey Doctor’s mission is: To collaborate, create, and reach out, promoting individuality and awareness, constantly raising the bar.
